        <div class="body">
            <p>Add these 2 lines of code to your "application.ini" and you will see the errors:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>resources.frontcontroller.throwExceptions          = 1
resources.frontcontroller.params.displayExceptions = 1</code></pre>

